OL,3,CRetired teaching assistant found with
OL,4,Cimages of child abuse on iPad
OL,6,FA retired teaching assistant who
OL,7,Fpossessed and distributed images
OL,8,Fdepicting child abuse tried to claim
OL,9,Fthe images were not indecent when
OL,10,Finterviewed by police.
OL,12,FDavid Wood, 69, was visited by police
OL,13,Fat his home in Cardiff on September 5
OL,14,Flast year and an iPad was seized and
OL,15,Fsearched. It resulted in the discovery
OL,16,Fof 12 category A indecent images and
OL,17,Ffour category B indecent images, which
OL,18,Fhad been downloaded between 2023 and
OL,19,F2024.
