OL,3,CRetired teaching assistant found with
OL,4,Cimages of child abuse on iPad
OL,6,FA sentencing hearing at Cardiff
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday heard
OL,8,Fthe images and videos depicted
OL,9,Fchildren aged between eight and 15-
OL,10,Fyears-old.
OL,12,FDuring his police interview, Wood said
OL,13,Fhe did not consider the images to be
OL,14,Findecent.
OL,16,FHe said he was attracted to boys over
OL,17,F14-years-old, and believed the
OL,18,Fchildren in the images were between 15
OL,19,Fand 16-years-old. The defendant said
OL,20,Fhe "did not realise" the images were
OL,21,Fillegal.
