OL,3,CRetired teaching assistant found with
OL,4,Cimages of child abuse on iPad
OL,6,FWood, of Hunter Street, Butetown,
OL,7,Flater pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,8,Fpossessing indecent images of
OL,9,Fchildren.JThe court heard he has no
OL,10,Fprevious convictions.
OL,12,FIn mitigation, the court was told the
OL,13,Fdefendant had previously worked as a
OL,14,Fteaching assistant at a secondary
OL,15,Fschool, but the offences were
OL,16,Fcommitted once he had retired.
OL,18,FIt was said Wood was a frequent user
OL,19,Fof social media and had begun speaking
OL,20,Fto individuals in the USA.
