OL,3,CRetired teaching assistant found with
OL,4,Cimages of child abuse on iPad
OL,6,FSentencing, district judge Hayes said:
OL,7,F"This has caused me a great deal of
OL,8,Fconcern, primarily you have come to
OL,9,Fthe attention of the police for having
OL,10,Fdistributed indecent images.
OL,12,F"You were interviewed and made some
OL,13,Fdisturbing comments that you did not
OL,14,Fconsider the images to be indecent,
OL,15,Fbut you admitted the offences."
OL,17,FThe judge said there was a "realistic
OL,18,Fprospect of rehabilitation" in the
OL,19,Fdefendant's case, primarily due to his
OL,20,Fprevious good character.
