OL,6,FWood was sentenced to 40 weeks
OL,7,Fimprisonment, suspended for two years.
OL,9,FThe defendant was made subject to a
OL,10,Frehabilitation activity requirement of
OL,11,F20 days, sex offender notification
OL,12,Frequirements and a Sexual Harm
OL,13,FPrevention Order for 10 years.
OL,15,FHe was also ordered to pay #85 in
OL,16,Fcosts and a #154 victim surcharge.
